page.title: 24Food shops in havant.
page.content:
In Havant the only food shop was Waitrose in 1986! Next door to Waitrose there used to be a news store which was also popular but now it is a Post office. In 2011 the most popular takeaway in Havant is a Chinese restaurant called the Golden Town. In 2011 The most popular food shop is Tesco. There are 10 Grocery stores in Havant.


Holly and Megan
